        {
            "title": "全日收市︱連跌5日 恒指跌137點報23462點 九倉、太古績後齊受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午市先挫後收復部份失地，卻未能擺脫五連跌的狀況；兩隻綜合企業股九倉(00004)與太古(00019)績後齊受壓。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：九倉官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230718-174303_source-web_00004-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：九倉官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230718-174303_source-web_00004-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：九倉官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早稍為高開16點後，原本只在10天線(最新約為23565點)升或跌百多點爭持，午後初段卻現明顯跌勢，跌幅最多擴大至401點，低見23198點，連20天線(最新約為23337點)也失守，隨後開始陸續收復失地，於20天線失而復得，但卻受制10天線。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指最後收報23462點，跌137點或0.58%；5日累計共跌907點或3.72%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數今日明顯跑輸，收跌97點或1.67%，報5747點；國企指數跌41點或0.48%，報8640點。主板成交進一步縮減至2338.33億元，較昨天再少逾400億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14773845-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e9%80%a3%e8%b7%8c5%e6%97%a5-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c137%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b123462%e9%bb%9e-%e4%b9%9d%e5%80%89%e3%80%81%e5%a4%aa%e5%8f%a4%e7%b8%be%e5%be%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-web_HKStock-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-13 16:20:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬指收跌13點 深指跌0.99% 煤炭股逆市升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地A股於午市尋底後跌勢放緩，整個下午差不多原地踏步；煤炭板塊見資金流入，中國神華(01088)A股(601088.SH)收升 %。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國神華官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230823_FI_source-web_中國神華704.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國神華官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230823_FI_source-web_中國神華704.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國神華官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早初段經過一輪好淡爭持後，於早市後段進入下降軌，跌勢延續至午後，最低曾見3341點，跌30點，後段走勢逐步好轉；滬指最後收報 點，跌幅收窄至跌13點或0.39%，成交6362.12億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指亦於午後尋底，低位10677點，跌165點，於收市前1小時開始轉勢；深指最後收報10736點，跌107點或0.99%，成交9705.17億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌15點或0.4%，以3911點收市；創業板指數跌25點或1.15%，報2166點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中煤能源官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230825_FI_source-web_01898.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中煤能源官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230825_FI_source-web_01898.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中煤能源官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">煤炭板塊逆市向好，中國神華A股收報37.22元，升3.59%；中煤能源(01898)A股(601898.SH)也升3.77%，報10.45元；兗礦能源(01171)A股(600188.SH)升2.55%，報13.65元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">芯片股再次受壓，中芯國際A股(688981.SH)跌3.05%，報92.98元；寒武紀(688256.SH)亦跌4.14%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14773513-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c13%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c0-99-%e7%85%a4%e7%82%ad%e8%82%a1%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250206_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-13 15:10:41",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "百威亞太據報今年擬裁數千職位以降營運成本15%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">《彭博》引述消息指，百威亞太(01876)計劃今年裁減數以千計職位，望能削減營運成本約15%，應對中國市場疲弱的需求。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"百威亞太2023年度年報封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/933x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240506_FI_source-web_01876-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"百威亞太2023年度年報封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/933x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240506_FI_source-web_01876-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">百威亞太2023年度年報封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司早前公布2024年度業績，純利退14.79%，但仍提升派息，另外又宣布易帥，委任中國國籍的程衍俊接替楊克擔任首席執行官及聯席主席，由4月1日起生效。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報道指，百威亞太早已開始裁員以減低成本，去年已在2.5萬多名員工中裁減16%人手。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14773477-%e7%99%be%e5%a8%81%e4%ba%9e%e5%a4%aa%e6%93%9a%e5%a0%b1%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e6%93%ac%e8%a3%81%e6%95%b8%e5%8d%83%e8%81%b7%e4%bd%8d%e4%bb%a5%e9%99%8d%e7%87%9f%e9%81%8b%e6%88%90%e6%9c%ac15",
